            "title": "華爾街期貨於耶穌受難日休市前保持穩定;聚焦就業數據",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Q6h6QwxW6sSH1MqrHXbmsg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA6U04V_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 美國股指期貨週四晚間小幅走高,在耶穌受難日市場假期前趨於穩定,投資者評估地緣政治發展,並為當日稍後公布的美國勞動市場關鍵報告做好準備。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至美國東部時間20:19(格林威治標準時間00:19),<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"標普500指數期貨\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:標普500指數期貨;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://in.investing.com/indices/us-spx-500-futures?utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_campaign=yahoo-hk\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">標普500指數期貨</a>基本持平於6,624.50點,納斯達克100指數期貨穩定於24,223.00點。道指期貨同樣持平於46,748.0點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">華爾街常規交易時段收盤漲跌互現。標普500指數在震盪交易後收盤幾乎持平,納斯達克綜合指數上漲0.2%。道瓊工業平均指數下跌0.1%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-ea494d23-77ba-3bb6-a6d1-c1ee1068591c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在伊朗外交部表示正與阿曼起草一項管理霍爾木茲海峽航運交通的協議後,午後交易時段投資者情緒有所改善。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">盤中早些時候,市場因總統唐納德·川普的言論而受到干擾,他表示華盛頓將在\"未來兩到三週\"加大對伊朗的打擊力度。缺乏明確的時間表以及進一步升級的前景為股票、大宗商品和貨幣市場注入了波動性。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">焦點現在轉向週五稍後公布的美國非農就業報告,預計該報告將為勞動市場強度和聯準會政策路徑提供新線索。若數據強於預期,可能強化利率將在較長時間內維持高位的押注,而疲弱的數據則可能支持今年稍後降息的預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由於市場週五因耶穌受難日休市,流動性可能保持低迷,可能放大市場波動。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
